</div><div id="shopify-section-1515782760835" class="shopify-section"><div data-section-id="1515782760835" data-section-type="alternating-content">
  
    

    

    <div class="module-wrapper style-green border">
      <div class="module home-left-right-features">
        <div class="module-body">

          <div class="home-left-right-feature clearfix media-aligned-right">
            <div class="home-left-right-section home-left-right-text ">
              
                <h3 class="module-title home-left-right-titles">
                  How Do Sundots Work?
                </h3>
              

              
                <div class="module-content home-left-right-content">
                  Sundots use polypodium leucotomos, a fern extract from Ecuador backed by 30+ years of sun protection research. The evidence is clear from over a dozen human studies - when taken like a vitamin, this fern  helps to provide all-over protection from sun damage.
<br><br>
<p style="font-size:23px"><b>"Polypodium leucotomos has proven effects in the prevention and treatment of UV-related skin damage."</b></p>
<p style="font-size:15px"><i>–Photochemical &amp; Photobiological Sciences. 2010 Apr;9(4):559-63</i></p>
                </div>
              

              
            </div>
            <div class="home-left-right-section home-left-right-media">
              
                
                  <img class="home-left-right-image" src="//web.archive.org/web/20180401011400im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2701/0262/files/0962-1020x700_1320x900.jpg?v=1520187567" alt="">
                
              

              
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
</div>

