                <h3 class="module-title home-left-right-titles">
                  Over 30+ Years Of Use Supporting Safety
                </h3>
              

              
                <div class="module-content home-left-right-content">
                  Polypodium has been used for decades for a variety of related inflammatory skin health issues like vitiligo and psoriasis. <b>Over 30+ years of study and use, polypodium has been shown to be safe, even at doses much higher than Sundots.</b>
 
<br><br>
<p style="font-size:23px"><b>"Polypodium leucotomos has been used in the management of inflammatory skin diseases for more than 
30 years without significant side effects.”</b></p>
<p style="font-size:15px"><i>–The Journal of American Academy of Dermatology. 2004; 50(1): 41-49</i></p>
                </div>
              

              
            </div>
            <div class="home-left-right-section home-left-right-media">
              
                
                  <img class="home-left-right-image" src="//web.archive.org/web/20180401011400im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2701/0262/files/0004-1020x700_1320x900.jpg?v=1520187719" alt="">
                
              

              
